...@nodes

# ────────────────────────────────────────────
# Founder dynamics inside Pied Piper
# ────────────────────────────────────────────
piedpiper.founders.richard -> piedpiper.middleout: wrote it {class: signature}
piedpiper.founders.jared -> piedpiper.founders.richard: believes in {class: money}
piedpiper.founders.erlich -> piedpiper.middleout: claims credit {class: quirk; style.stroke-dash: 4}
piedpiper.founders.erlich -> piedpiper.pipey: designed the mascot {class: quirk}

# ────────────────────────────────────────────
# Engineering -> the algorithm
# ────────────────────────────────────────────
piedpiper.eng.gilfoyle -> piedpiper.middleout: optimizes {class: optimize}
piedpiper.eng.dinesh -> piedpiper.middleout: also optimizes {class: optimize}
piedpiper.eng.dinesh <-> piedpiper.eng.gilfoyle: subtweets {class: hostile; style.stroke-dash: 3}
piedpiper.eng.bighead <-> piedpiper.eng.gilfoyle: rooftop tutoring {class: whim}

# ────────────────────────────────────────────
# Inner-to-inner: pipeline data flow
# ────────────────────────────────────────────
piedpiper.middleout -> pipeline.ingestor: powers {class: signature}
pipeline.ingestor -> pipeline.weissman: score it {class: data}
pipeline.weissman -> pipeline.tiptotip: optimize {class: data}
pipeline.tiptotip -> pipeline.output: emit blob {class: data}
pipeline.output -> pipeline.cache: warm cache {class: cache}
pipeline.cache -> pipeline.blobstore: spill to disk {class: cache; style.stroke-dash: 4}
pipeline.output -> pipeline.blobstore: persist {class: data; style.stroke-width: 1}

# ────────────────────────────────────────────
# Outer-container connections (whole-thing -> whole-thing)
# ────────────────────────────────────────────
piedpiper -> pipeline: ships {class: ship}
pipeline -> newinternet: distributes via {class: ship}
piedpiper.founders.richard -> newinternet: dreams of {class: ship; style.stroke-dash: 4; style.stroke-width: 1}

# ────────────────────────────────────────────
# Decentralized fan-out (inner -> peers in another container)
# ────────────────────────────────────────────
pipeline.blobstore -> newinternet.phone: shard {class: shard}
pipeline.blobstore -> newinternet.fridge: shard {class: shard}
pipeline.blobstore -> newinternet.condorcam: shard {class: shard; style.stroke-dash: 3}

# ────────────────────────────────────────────
# Hooli vs Pied Piper
# ────────────────────────────────────────────
hooli.gavin -> piedpiper: sues {class: lawsuit; target-arrowhead.shape: diamond; target-arrowhead.style.filled: true}
hooli.gavin -> hooli.nucleus: demands wins {class: hostile}
hooli.nucleus -> piedpiper.middleout: tries to clone {class: theft}
hooli.nucleus -> hooli.hoolicloud: uploads telemetry {class: data; style.stroke-width: 1}
hooli.endframe -> piedpiper.middleout: literally stole the code {class: theft; style.stroke-width: 2; style.stroke-dash: 5; target-arrowhead.shape: cf-many}
hooli.gavin -> hooli.hoolixyz: incubates {class: hostile}
hooli.hoolixyz -> piedpiper.eng.bighead: poaches {class: theft}

# ────────────────────────────────────────────
# Money flows
# ────────────────────────────────────────────
money.russ -> piedpiper: tres comas {class: investment; target-arrowhead.shape: cf-one-required}
money.raviga -> piedpiper: Series B {class: investment; target-arrowhead.shape: cf-one}
money.laurie -> money.raviga: managing partner {class: money}
money.monica -> money.raviga: junior partner {class: money}
money.monica <-> piedpiper.founders.richard: secretly rooting for {class: hedge}
money.raviga -> hooli: also invests {class: hedge}

# ────────────────────────────────────────────
# Whimsical extras
# ────────────────────────────────────────────
piedpiper.founders.erlich -> aviato: previously exited {class: whim}
piedpiper.eng.bighead -> nothotdog: co-founded? {class: whim; style.stroke-dash: 3}
nothotdog -> seefood: powers {class: shard}
seefood -> hooli.hoolixyz: pivot acquisition {class: hedge; style.stroke-dash: 4}
newinternet.condorcam -> hooli.gavin: live feed of his pet {class: quirk; style.stroke-dash: 3; target-arrowhead.shape: circle; target-arrowhead.style.filled: true}
